Privacy Policy for EduPlay World

Effective Date: 22-04-2025

EduPlay World ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our Android mobile application EduPlay World ("App").

By using EduPlay World, you agree to the practices described in this policy. If you do not agree with the terms, please do not use the app.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect and process the following types of information:

a. Personal Information
We do not collect personally identifiable information unless explicitly provided by you (e.g., when registering an account, contacting support).

b. Non-Personal Information
We may collect anonymous usage data, including:

Device type and model

Operating system and version

App version and usage statistics

Interaction logs within the app

c. Children's Privacy
EduPlay World is designed for educational purposes and may be used by children with parental or school supervision. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13 without parental consent.

2. How We Use Your Information
We may use the collected information to:

Improve the user experience and app performance

Monitor and analyze usage trends

Fix bugs and ensure technical functionality

Respond to inquiries or customer support requests

3. Sharing of Your Information
We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.

We may share data:

With trusted service providers who assist in operating our app (e.g., analytics tools)

If required by law or to protect our rights

4. Third-Party Services
Our app may use third-party services (e.g., Google Analytics for Firebase, AdMob) that collect information in accordance with their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review those policies separately.

5. Data Security
We use industry-standard security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

